          "content": {
            "mimeType": "text/html; charset=UTF-8",
            "size": 5525,
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n\n<title>Spellenspeciaalzaak Moenen &amp; Mariken Nijmegen &raquo; Aeons End 2nd Ed. (ENG)</title>\n<meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"application/xhtml+xml; charset=UTF-8\" \\>\n<!--tirei o meta, lembra-te de o trazer de volta-->\n\n<!--<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/editor.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/lightbox.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/profile.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/html.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/layout.css.php\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/form.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/borders.css.php\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/bammcms.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/menu.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/agenda.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>-->\n\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/foundation.min.css\" \\>\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/normalize.css\" \\>\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/styleMP.css\" \\>\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/slick/slick.css\" \\>\n</head>\n\n    <body> \n    <section id=\"productDetail\">\n        <div class=\"productDetailBox\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"small-12 columns\">\n                    <div class=\"row detailProdHead\">\n                        <div class=\"small-10 columns\">\n                            <h3 class=\"artikelname\">Aeons End 2nd Ed. (ENG)</h3>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"small-2 columns\">\n                            <div class=\"closeMandje\"><p>X</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <article class=\"product\">\n                        <div class=\"row\">\n                            <div class=\"small-4 columns prodDetailImg\">\n                                <img src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/_productpics/792273251554.jpg\" border=\"0\" width=\"200px\" \\>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"small-8 columns\">\n                                <ul>\n                                    <li>Artikelcode: 792273251554</li>\n                                    <li>Categorie: Bord- & Kaartspellen</li>\n                                    <li>Spelsysteem: Aeons End</li>\n                                    <li>Prijs: &euro; 70,95</li>\n                                    <li>Op voorraad: Ja</li>\n                                    <li>Spelers: 1 - 4</li>\n                                    <li>Speltype : Cooperatief</li>\n                                    <li>Leeftijd: 14+</li>\n                                    <li>Minuten: 30 - 60</li>\n                                    <li>Ontwerper: Kevin Riley</li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"row\">\n                            <div class=\"small-12 columns prodText\">\n                                <p>Aeon's End is a cooperative game that explores the deckbuilding genre with a number of innovative mechanisms, including a variable turn order system that simulates the chaos of an attack, and deck management rules that require careful planning with every discarded card. Players will struggle to defend Gravehold from The Nameless and their hordes using unique abilities, powerful spells, and, most importantly of all, their collective wits.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </article>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <footer>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.manuelcalapez.com\" target=\"_blank\">front-end design and development by manuel calapez</a></p>\n    </footer>\n    \n    <script src=\"//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/tooltip/wz_tooltip.js\"> </script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/foundation.min.js\"> </script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/mainJS.js\"> </script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/slick/slick.min.js\"> </script>\n \n    <script>\n      $(document).foundation();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n\n\n"
